data.description: It's fitting with the home on this corner lot, there's a four-way stop for all eyes to lock on it! This location is paramount, just minutes away from Vassar and Frankenmuth and a chip shot from an "up-north" style golf course. The more than 1600 square foot house has a fine-flowing open concept, three bedrooms and two full bathrooms, including a private one in the primary suite. The curb-appeal on this almost one acre lot has plenty of space for outside activities, like a nice fire on one of the upcoming summer nights. With the country feel just down the road from all major necessities, stop in to check it out!
